Version 2.1.01 (02-04-2014)
-Search bar, now integrates with qTranslate

Version 2.1.0 (02-03-2014)
-CyberChimps logo removed
-404 page blank footer bugfix
-Losts of translation bugs fixed
-Translation capability added to lots of static texts
-Fixed search bar text localization problem
-Post format images clour has changed to fancy blue
-Added capability of using shortcodes in widgets
-qTranslate integration header menu links has solved
-Attention! Theme update feature of WordPress blocked,
because of that Neuro has new 3.x updates.
If you updated Neuro accidentally, it'd be a disaster.
So, theme update notifications must be blocked.

